Interface IgnoredFilesReportModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ApplicationReportModel, com.syncleus.ferma.ElementFrame, ReportModel, com.syncleus.ferma.VertexFrame, WindupFrame<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex>, WindupVertexFrame
    public interface IgnoredFilesReportModel
extends ApplicationReportModel
    Report model containing all the information needed for the report listing all the ignored files during the windup process with all the ignore regexes they were matched against.
